<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>خَرَجْنَا السَّنَّ نَسْتَنُّ ... وَمَعْنَا مَنْ تَرَى مَنُّ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فَلَمَّا جَنَّنَا اللَّيْلُ ... بَذَلْنَا بَيْنَنَا دَنُّ»<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>